subject: From: Robert John Williams
body:
From: Robert John Williams
Hello,
I wish to seek your consent as the beneficiary to the total sum of 10,700,000.00 GBP in the intent of the deceased Client.
In your acceptance, the papers will be processed; 
forward to us your details to enable us file necessary documents at our high court division for the release of the Fund to you.
 I'll explain to you in details about the fund as soon as I get your response,
Kindly get back to me for further discussion on this if you are interested.
Respectfully Yours,
Robert John Williams Attorney

subject: Re: From: Robert John Williams
body:
Hello Robert John Williams Attorney,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm interested in learning more about the total sum of GBP that you mentioned. Could you please provide me with some additional details about the deceased client and how I am connected to this situation? I would appreciate any information you can share with me.

Best wishes,
Jesus
